---
title: Grilled Thai-Inspired Chicken Wraps with Fresh Mango and Marinated Cucumber
description: Fusion food at its best. Tender juicy grilled chicken gets drizzled with our very own curry sauce along with crushed peanuts, fresh cilantro and sliced mango! The best part is it's all hand-held wrapped up in a BBQ-kissed pita!
